          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2260-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened to a maple syrup-like consistency</p>",
